H233699本票1張（面額53萬5000元，發票人余東諺、\r\n     朱唯秀）（109偵7006號卷第155頁）　 \r\n (三)現金新臺幣1萬5000元","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/109%2c%e6%98%93%2c3107%2c20220830%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,109,易,3107,20220830,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"易","JNO":"3107","JDATE":"20220830","JTITLE":"恐嚇取財等"}